caption.text: DECOLORIZE_OFFENSIVE  Dear IGers Well, it's been a long time since our last Offensive (yeah, the #Ortonoffensive was pretty cool, there's no denying it ) and so we thought it was about time to have another blast. This time we'll have the #decolorize_offensive.   The idea is to have B&W pics with a splash of color. There are countless apps that can be used to achieve that and most of them are free!!!   We have a bold project in mind. For one hour we wanna make the popular page all Decolorized pics. It's a global enterprise and it's gonna happen this Saturday night/Sunday morning depending on your time zone.   The idea is to post Decolorized pics under #decolorize_offensive. All pics posted under #decolorize_offensive  will be liked because we want the biggest possible number of Decolorized pics on pop page. So don't forget to go to the   #decolorize_offensive page to vote on the other pics after posting yours. There's no pic limit. The important thing is to be a part of it and have fun and of course it's a great opportunity to have a pic on pop page too   If you don't know any app to get that effect let me suggest some (there are lots of them): Colorsplash Picture effect magic Decolorizer Colorup Colorblast  Our schedule time is: August 27 Saturday US West coast 6 to 7 pm        East Coast 9 to 10 pm Brazil 10 to 11 pm   August 28 Sunday Australia 11am to 12 pm Japan.  10 to 11 am Singapore 9 to 10 am London 2 to 3 am France 3 to 4 am Turkey 4 to 5 am Moscow 5 to 6 am India 7 to 8 am   For our Europe IGers, we are really sorry for the inconvenience of the time, again :(:(:(
